# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Global ignores (apply anywhere)
# ------------------------------------------------------------

# Cargo build artifacts
-target/

# VCS / editor noise
-.fspec
-.git/
-.idea/
-.vscode/


# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Workspace root files
# ------------------------------------------------------------
+/Cargo.toml
+/Cargo.lock

# Common root metadata (optional but typical)
+/README*
+/LICENSE*
+/.gitignore
+/rustfmt.toml


# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Rust source files (anywhere, unless ignored)
# ------------------------------------------------------------

# All Rust source must be snake_case
+{snake_case}.rs


# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Crates layout (workspace crates/)
# ------------------------------------------------------------

# NOTE: these crate specific contents might be better handled 
# by crate internal .fspec, adding or overriding rules from the
# workspace root.
# Each crate must have a Cargo.toml (but no Cargo.lock here)
+/crates/{crate:kebab-case}/Cargo.toml

# Source tree exists and may contain subdirectories
+/crates/{crate:kebab-case}/src/**/

# Only snake_case Rust files allowed under src/
+/crates/{crate:kebab-case}/src/**/{snake_case}.rs
